PrecisEnactment of the WITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL ORDER (DAWSON FIRST NATION, Y.T.) - which provides for the withdrawal from disposal of specific lands in the Klondike Valley area of the Yukon Territory in order to facilitate the settlement of native land claims made by the Dawson First Nation.
